Package abi

Class AbiFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • abi.AbiFunction
  • public class AbiFunction
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to represent a function inside an ABI. It does not store all the information, but only:
    • Type
    • Name
    • Inputs
    • Outputs
    Where inputs and outputs are lists of IOElement
